::KitKat::

She stood in front of Quickstrike. Her body covered in mech fluid and 
blood.  She was proud of herself.  She faught off a bear and won. She 
smiled.  "I found something to cure my boredom. But now I have to get 
cleaned up.  Where are the CR chambers?"
